             were indicted for <rs id="t18320405-319-off1847" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18320405-319-off1847" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320405-319-off1847" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18320405-319-cd1848" type="crimeDate">4th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-319-off1847 t18320405-319-cd1848"></join>, 1 hat, value 9s., and 1 handkerchief, value 1s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18320405-319-victim2642" type="victimName">
                     Charles 
                     Bland
                  <interp inst="t18320405-319-victim2642" type="surname" value="Bland"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320405-319-victim2642" type="given" value="Charles"></interp>
